room_title: Escape room "Classified" by Escape Room BCS in College Station
review: Classified is a fun room for new escapees.  It has some really cool aspects.  But when you are a 25+ escape room escapee, it's not that impressive.  It has too many locks and not enough "wow" factors for experienced players.

room_title: Escape room "Classified" by Escape Room BCS in College Station
review: We played the Classified room and made it out just in time! We had three people. There were lots of different puzzles so each of us got a chance to figure a few out. The staff was friendly and the instructions and clues were clear and understandable. We had a good time. Would definitely come back to try some of their other puzzles!
